text: Francisco Hernández can refer to the following people: *Francisco Hernández de Córdoba (founder of Nicaragua) (1475-1526) *Francisco Hernández de Córdoba (Yucatán conquistador) (died 1517) *Francisco Hernández de Chaves Spanish explorer, 16th century *Francisco Hernández Girón Spanish explorer, executed December 1554 *Francisco Hernández de Toledo (1514-1587) Spanish botanist
title: Francisco Hernández
